        12.5V5a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V2zm2 3v7.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.5 14h9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V5H2zm13-3H1v2h14V2zM5 7.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h5a.5.5 
        0 0 1 0 1h-5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5z</Geometry>
